    "Future implementations leveraging multiple VIs into a multivariate detection platform would likely lead to improved, robust detection over the duration of the grow out.",
    "For example, joining VI features that are more sensitive to early deficiencies such as NDWI with those that are sensitive to later changes like GNDVI along with mid-stage detection indices (NDRE) could lead to sustained detection.",
